I want to take time out of the week to highlight the importance of being mobile and making it part of your journey. The less mobile we become, the more in pain and prone to injury we will be.

Take these few stretches you can do at home with one tool you can always find. Depending on your own current mobility, these movements may start at an easier angle or even further from the wall.

Start with what you have, and stay consistent. Watch what happens when you make this a daily habit.
